OL,5,G0950 The Secret Life of Trees
OL,6,     FMichael Palin narrates this
OL,7,     Fcaptivating series, discovering
OL,8,     Fhow trees have developed the art
OL,9,     Fof growing and ageing gracefully
OL,10,     Fas they pass from their early
OL,11,     Fyears into middle age.
OL,12,G1050 The Secret Life of Trees
OL,13,     FMichael Palin narrates as we
OL,14,     Ffollow trees into old age and
OL,15,     Fdiscover how some trees alive
OL,16,     Ftoday are as old as the pyramids.
OL,17,     FAnd a look at how a dying tree
OL,18,     Fcreates new life.
